lyrics:
[Verse]
Dr. Herbstman, working all day long
Fixing teeth, making patients strong
But he's got a dream, just can't wait
To finish that crown, then he'll bake, bake, bake

[Chorus]
Dr. Herbstman, he's got a dental crown to do
Once it's complete, he'll bid us adieu
He's got cookies to make, pies to create
Dr. Herbstman just can't wait, wait, wait
